column3: List all boardgames by GMT.
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbo:publisher res:GMT_Games }

column3: Who developed Skype?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Skype dbo:developer ?uri. }

column3: Which people were born in Heraklion?
column5: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX onto: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type onto:Person ; onto:birthPlace <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heraklion>. }

column3: In which U.S. state is Area 51 located?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Area_51 dbo:location ?uri . ?uri dbo:country res:United_States. }

column3: Who is the mayor of New York City?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:New_York_City dbo:leaderName ?uri }

column3: Which countries have places with more than two caves?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?cave rdf:type dbo:Cave ; dbo:location ?uri . ?uri rdf:type dbo:Country } GROUP BY ?uri HAVING ( COUNT(?cave) > 2 )

column3: Where did Abraham Lincoln die?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Abraham_Lincoln dbo:deathPlace ?uri. }

column3: Which airports does Air China serve?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Air_China dbo:targetAirport ?uri }

column3: Give me all actors starring in movies directed by and starring William Shatner.
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?x dbo:director res:William_Shatner ; dbo:starring res:William_Shatner { ?x dbo:starring ?uri } UNION { ?x dbp:starring ?uri } }

column3: What are the official languages of the Philippines?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Philippines dbo:officialLanguage ?uri }

column3: Give me all Danish films.
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Film ; dbo:country res:Denmark }

column3: Which movies starring Brad Pitt were directed by Guy Ritchie?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Film ; dbo:starring res:Brad_Pitt ; dbo:director res:Guy_Ritchie }

column3: Give me the grandchildren of Bruce Lee.
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Bruce_Lee dbo:child ?child . ?child <http://dbpedia.org/property/children> ?uri }

column3: Which other weapons did the designer of the Uzi develop?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Weapon ; dbp:designer ?x . res:Uzi dbp:designer ?x FILTER ( ?uri != res:Uzi ) }

column3: Who is the owner of Universal Studios?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Universal_Studios dbo:owner ?uri }

column3: Which state of the USA has the highest population density?
column5: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatStatesOfTheUnitedStates ; dbp:densityrank ?rank } ORDER BY ASC(?rank) LIMIT 1

column3: Which monarchs were married to a German?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Monarch ; dbo:spouse ?spouse { ?spouse dbo:birthPlace res:Germany } UNION { ?spouse dbo:birthPlace ?p . ?p dbo:country res:Germany } }

column3: Which organizations were founded in 1950?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Organisation { ?uri dbo:formationYear ?date } UNION { ?uri dbo:foundingYear ?date } UNION { ?uri dbp:foundation ?date } UNION { ?uri dbp:formation ?date } FILTER regex(?date, ^1950) }

column3: Who created the comic Captain America?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Captain_America dbo:creator ?uri }

column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbo:mission res:Apollo_14 }

column3: Who wrote the book The pillars of the Earth?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:The_Pillars_of_the_Earth dbo:author ?uri }

column3: Which state of the United States of America has the highest density?
column5: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbp:densityrank ?density } ORDER BY ASC(?density) LIMIT 1

column3: Which spaceflights were launched from Baikonur?

column3: Give me a list of all trumpet players that were bandleaders.
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbo:occupation res:Bandleader ; dbo:instrument res:Trumpet }

column3: Which U.S. states are in the same timezone as Utah?
column5: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Utah dbp:timezone ?x . ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatStatesOfTheUnitedStates ; dbp:timezone ?x FILTER ( ?uri != res:Utah ) }

column3: Which U.S. states possess gold minerals?
column5: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatStatesOfTheUnitedStates ; dbp:mineral ?mineral FILTER regex(?mineral, gold, i) }

column3: Who is the daughter of Ingrid Bergman married to?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Ingrid_Bergman dbo:child ?child . ?child <http://dbpedia.org/property/spouse> ?uri }

column3: How deep is Lake Placid?
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT DISTINCT ?n WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lake_Placid_(Texas)> dbo:maximumDepth ?n }

column3: Show me all museums in London.

column3: What are the top-10 action role-playing video games according to IGN?
